| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-3458 — Recovery Inhibition (flocker)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 61e6eb94-d04c-5c6a-8f84-9dcf3d8e23fd"
